554
00:34:29.574 --> 00:34:30.708
Oh.

555
00:34:30.784 --> 00:34:32.794
Hey. You work here now?

556
00:34:33.078 --> 00:34:35.004
You drink coffee now?

557
00:34:36.039 --> 00:34:38.800
Yeah. I mean. I just sort of started.

558
00:34:39.667 --> 00:34:41.969
Look at our little Clay. all grown up.

559
00:34:44.005 --> 00:34:45.473
So. do you want one now?

560
00:34:46.633 --> 00:34:50.594
Oh. right. Uh... A small
