571
00:35:23.795 --> 00:35:24.929
I remember.

572
00:35:26.840 --> 00:35:28.307
No. wait. I forgot.

573
00:35:29.092 --> 00:35:32.261
When I was little. I used to cry
every time we drove over a bridge.

574
00:35:32.262 --> 00:35:33.428
I don't know why.

575
00:35:33.429 --> 00:35:35.472
My mom used to try to distract me...

576
00:35:35.473 --> 00:35:38.433
And she would tell you to look for
a purple alligator in the water.

577
00:35:38.434 --> 00:35:41.737
and you'd be so busy looking
you'd forget you were scared.

578
00:35:44.023 --> 00:35:45.616
Yeah. that's the story.

579
00:35:51.114 --> 00:35:52.373
It's on the house.

580
00:35:54.200 --> 00:35:55.418
Oh.

581
00:36:03.835 --> 00:36:05.669
Do you think it might have been

582
00:36:05.670 --> 00:36:07.379
Clay who tore the posters down?

583
00:36:07.380 --> 00:36:08.881
