just not something he would do.

585
00:36:12.510 --> 00:36:13.677
Hmm.

586
00:36:13.678 --> 00:36:17.097
Can you think of anyone else who
might have wanted to act out like that.

587
00:36:17.098 --> 00:36:20.642
