No. I... I know it's
hit a lot of kids hard.

590
00:36:26.983 --> 00:36:28.609
You two were friends with Hannah?

591
00:36:28.610 --> 00:36:29.902
Well. "friends" is...

592
00:36:29.903 --> 00:36:32.196
