Did she ever talk about
how she was feeling?

596
00:36:41.331 --> 00:36:44.258
Most of the time she
seemed pretty chill to me.

597
00:36:44.626 --> 00:36:47.386
I guess there were
times she was emotional.

598
00:36:48.296 --> 00:36:49.796
But who isn't?

599
00:36:49.797 --> 00:36:51.349
Yeah. that's true.

600
00:36:51.674 --> 00:36:57.638
