633
00:38:24.142 --> 00:38:26.601
Well. you should be.

634
00:38:26.602 --> 00:38:28.854
But I mean. seriously.
it was just a list.

635
00:38:28.855 --> 00:38:30.605
Like. a stupid high school thing.

636
00:38:30.606 --> 00:38:33.951
That fucking list. I wish I
never touched that fucking list.

637
00:38:34.902 --> 00:38:36.049
