646
00:38:52.879 --> 00:38:54.639
They thought it was funny and stuff.

647
00:38:55.423 --> 00:38:58.300
My dad was relieved
that I had male friends.

648
00:38:58.301 --> 00:39:02.355
Also. didn't totally suck at school
that Justin Foley liked me back then.

649
00:39:03.264 --> 00:39:04.815
Okay. back then.

650
00:39:05.516 --> 00:39:07.017
