And the guys already thought
that we were. and I wanted to.

662
00:39:43.638 --> 00:39:46.148
You know? I-I loved her.

663
00:39:46.557 --> 00:39:49.360
And it did piss Jessica
off. but not at me.

664
00:39:49.644 --> 00:39:50.811
At Hannah.

665
00:39:50.812 --> 00:39:52.255
Alex did this on his own.

666
00:39:52.280 --> 00:39:54.874
