667
00:39:54.899 --> 00:39:56.128
Enjoy it.

668
00:39:56.153 --> 00:39:57.317
'Cause you will. won't you?

669
00:39:57.318 --> 00:39:59.161
'Cause that's what sluts do.

670
00:39:59.404 --> 00:40:00.538
Fuck you.

671
