It's just...

718
00:42:43.901 --> 00:42:45.327
It's real tight.

719
00:42:46.112 --> 00:42:48.497
In the store. It's tight in the store.

720
00:42:49.865 --> 00:42:53.335
I don't usually listen to
sophomore gossip. but. um...

721
